You follow a microfrontend-like, modular architecture that separates logic cleanly across:
- `Redesign/VizoraWeb` тАФ Admin/Web user interface
- `Redesign/VizoraTV` тАФ TV-facing display app
- `Redesign/VizoraMiddleware` тАФ Node.js backend, REST + Socket.IO server
- `Redesign/VizoraDisplay` тАФ Content rendering and media orchestration logic
- `Redesign/common` тАФ Shared logic and types used across all Vizora apps

