## ЁЯЫЖ SOCKET.IO REMINDER

- All apps now use **root namespace (`"/"`)**
- `ConnectionManager` in `@vizora/common` handles socket state, events, reconnection.
- Do not use or define `getSocketId()` manually тАФ use `connection.socket.id`.

